14:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Fireflies.ai and Sunsama share a solid foundation of core features including Task Management, Ai Assistant, Calendar, Integrations. Where Fireflies.ai pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Notes and Collaboration and Automation, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Fireflies.ai holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Sunsama scores 7/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
15:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Fireflies.ai offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Free, compared to Sunsama's starting price of $20/mo. Fireflies.ai has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Sunsama does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
